It is used to find out Users and Groups names and numeric ID’s (UID or GID) of the current user or any other user in the server.

id
id USER_NAME                                # display UID no, GID no, Group name  
id -u
id -u USER_NAME                             # display UID no
id -g USER_NAME                             # display GID no
id -G USER_NAME                             # Print all Group ID’s
id -ng USER_NAME
id -gn USER_NAME
id -nu USER_NAME
id -nG USER_NAME
id -r -g USER_NAME
id -r -u USER_NAME
id -r -G USER_NAME
